blog.name: jackoshadows
blog.title: Jak O' the Shadows
blog.description: I’m not going to swear an oath I can’t uphold. Talk about my father if you want. Tell me that’s the attitude that got him killed. But when enough people make false promises, words stop meaning anything. Then there are no more answers - only better and better lies. And lies won’t help us in this fight - Jon Snow.

tags: I saw some Jaime/Brienne fans talking about how it was a certainty that Dany dies and jaime becomes king because NCW loves the ending...
summary: What we think is going to happen next season...
title: What we think is going to happen next season...
body:
GOT cast : The ending is bittersweet, shocking, surprising, unexpected, you will never see it coming….

Jon/Sansa fans: Evil Dany, Arya slitting her throat, LF!Jon, Queen Sansa and Jonsa is the only thing that will be surprising and shocking to the general audience. It’s only us super intelligent meta writers who have figured this all out.

Jaime/Brienne fans: Everyone is going to die and Jaime and Brienne are going to sit on the Iron Throne and rule - that’s pretty much the only shocking//surprising ending, but it makes perfect sense you all. Jaime is a noble hero who has been on a redemption arc to the Iron Throne.

Jon/Dany fans: It must be Tyrion betraying Dany in some way and dying- would be shocking. Everyone thinks Jon/Dany is dying and so them living and sitting on the IT at the end will be surprising. People are not expecting a disney ending and so we will get a disney ending. Sike!

Arya/Gendry fans: It’s definitely these two - no one is going to see it coming and Robert’s Bastard is going to be become king and marry Arya and make her queen.

Hotpie fans: Yeah, everyone is going to die and Hotpie is going to take over. It’s the only ending that makes sense and would be totally surprising for everyone

King Bran fans: It’s going to happen! The betting sites tell me so!

SanSan fans : Sandor is Azor Ahai and Sansa is Nissa Nissa! It’s coming you guys!

Sansa/Tyrion fans - They are still married in the books for a reason, they make the perfect match  - everyone else dies and they take over! Shock! Surprise!

Littlefinger fans: It’s LF you guys! Master of chaos. He’s going nowhere. He’s going to suddenly show up with a cloth around his neck having survived the throat slitting and is going to win the Game of Thrones - suits the nihilism of GRRM’s world.

Jon/Arya fans: Shocking, Sudden, Unexpected things happening next season you say?
